text: Pavel Vasilievitch Moroz (born 26 February 1987) is a Russian volleyball player of Ukrainian origin, a member of Russia men's national volleyball team and Russian club Fakel Novy Urengoy. ==Career== ===Clubs=== In 2013 he went to Lokomotiv Novosibirsk.
